tourBios.exmtStatus: Finished T21 at 2015 Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament
tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T11 at the Florida Qualifying Tournament, with rounds of 71-69-67-65...Played in 12 events on Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada and made 10 cuts. Finished T8 at the Syncrude Boreal Open, fifth at the Wildfire Invitational, T8 at the Cape Breton Classic and seventh at the Freedom 55 Financial Championship.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Attended Penn State University for one semester before opting to turn pro. Notched one victory as a freshman, at the 2010 Maryland Intercollegiate.
tourBios.personal: Favorite pro teams are the New York Yankees and New York Rangers...Dream foursome would include his dad, Davis Love III and Tiger Woods...Marks his ball with a coin from his grandmother...Hopes to play Augusta National someday...Twitter account is @michael_cmiller.

tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T11 at Florida Q-School with rounds of 71-69-67-65. Made 10 cuts in 12 starts with four top 10s. First was T8 at The Syncrude Boreal in June. September was good month as he finished season with the final three top 10s: fifth place at the Wildfire Invitational with rounds of 65-68-66-70, T8 at the Cape Breton Classic and seventh place at the Freedom 55 Financial Championship.
tourBios.personal: Favorite pro teams are the New York Yankees and New York Rangers...Dream foursome would include his dad, Davis Love and Tiger Woods...Marks his ball with a coin from his grandmother...Hopes to play Augusta National someday...Twitter account is @michael_cmiller.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was 5th in 2015 at the Wildfire Invitational presented by PC Financial.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 18th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
